#: ../../../prop_inst/CPACK_WIX_ACL.rst:2
msgid "CPACK_WIX_ACL"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../prop_inst/CPACK_WIX_ACL.rst:6
msgid ""
"Specifies access permissions for files or directories installed by a WiX "
"installer."
msgstr "指定 WiX 安裝程式所安裝之檔案或目錄的存取權限。"

#: ../../../prop_inst/CPACK_WIX_ACL.rst:9
msgid ""
"The property can contain multiple list entries, each of which has to match "
"the following format."
msgstr "此屬性可以包含多個列表項目，每個項目必須符合以下格式。"

#: ../../../prop_inst/CPACK_WIX_ACL.rst:14
msgid "<user>[@<domain>]=<permission>[,<permission>]"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../prop_inst/CPACK_WIX_ACL.rst:16
msgid ""
"``<user>`` and ``<domain>`` specify the windows user and domain for which "
"the ``<Permission>`` element should be generated."
msgstr ""
"``<user>`` 和 ``<domain>`` 指定應為其產生 ``<Permission>`` 元素的 Windows 使"
"用者和網域。"

#: ../../../prop_inst/CPACK_WIX_ACL.rst:19
msgid ""
"``<permission>`` is any of the YesNoType attributes listed at: https://docs."
"firegiant.com/wix3/xsd/wix/permission/"
msgstr ""
"``<permission>`` 是 https://docs.firegiant.com/wix3/xsd/wix/permission/ 中列"
"出的任何 YesNoType 屬性。"

#: ../../../prop_inst/CPACK_WIX_ACL.rst:22
msgid ""
"The property is currently only supported by the :cpack_gen:`CPack WIX "
"Generator`."
msgstr "此屬性目前僅受 :cpack_gen:`CPack WIX Generator` 支援。"
